HEADWORD: Conferruminated
<hw>Con`fer*ru"mi*na`ted</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> }</mhw>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[L. <ets>conferruminare</ets> to cement. See
<er>Ferruminate</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Closely united by
